                <supplied reason="lost"><expan><abbr>D</abbr><ex>is</ex></expan></supplied> <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>anibus</ex></expan> </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/><supplied reason="lost">E</supplied>xorata <lb n="2"/><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/><supplied reason="lost"><expan><abbr>ann</abbr><ex>orum</ex></expan></supplied> XXIII <lb n="3"/><supplied reason="lost">hic sita</supplied> est <lb n="4"/><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/><supplied reason="lost">P</supplied>otens <lb n="5"/><supplied reason="lost"><expan><abbr>v</abbr><ex>ivus</ex></expan> sibi</supplied> et <expan><abbr>con</abbr><ex>iugi</ex></expan> <lb n="0"/><gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="line"/>
            </ab></div></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Zwei aneinanderpassende Fragmente vom rechten oberen Teil einer Grabstele. Zeile 1 befindet sich im Bildfeld oberhalb des Inschriftfeldes, darin Kranz mit Resten einer Büste(?). Oberhalb des Bildfeldes Rest eines Löwen. Zeile 1: TA-Ligatur. (B): Diebold: Z. 6 nicht angegeben.</p>
            </div>
